WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:56.400 --> 01:57.680
Tell that dog to come down here.

01:59.320 --> 02:00.720
He's coming down already.

02:04.400 --> 02:05.840
Maybe I should leave you here.

02:05.920 --> 02:07.280
I'm going to go.

02:09.199 --> 02:10.720
I thought we were having a barbecue.

02:11.360 --> 02:13.160
You seem quite happy to be here.

02:14.360 --> 02:15.560
All right. Go on.

02:15.640 --> 02:17.080
Give me my phone and bag.

02:17.160 --> 02:18.320
Hey.

02:18.400 --> 02:19.760
Can't you be more reserved?

02:20.400 --> 02:21.680
What's wrong now?

02:22.280 --> 02:23.360
I'm here for my boyfriend.

02:23.440 --> 02:24.920
Why should I be reserved?

02:25.000 --> 02:26.080
You're weird.

02:27.840 --> 02:29.480
Are you sure it was Duan Jiaxu

02:29.560 --> 02:30.680
who did the pursuing?

02:41.080 --> 02:42.560
What is that supposed to mean?

02:43.200 --> 02:44.640
I'm just asking.

02:45.800 --> 02:47.200
Don't spin any stories.

02:47.280 --> 02:48.680
Mind your language.

02:48.760 --> 02:51.080
I said I was just asking.

02:51.160 --> 02:52.480
You were implying something.

02:52.560 --> 02:53.600
I was asking…

02:54.640 --> 02:56.040
What are you arguing about?

02:58.520 --> 02:59.760
Get in the car.

02:59.840 --> 03:01.840
Ignore him. Let's go.

03:16.600 --> 03:17.680
Come here.

03:26.400 --> 03:27.760
Sorry for the long wait.

03:31.280 --> 03:32.400
Are you hungry?

03:32.480 --> 03:33.720
No.

03:35.920 --> 03:37.240
Are you hungry?

03:38.120 --> 03:39.000
Not yet.

03:49.000 --> 03:49.920
What?

03:51.280 --> 03:52.600
Do me a favor.

03:52.680 --> 03:54.200
Please don't do anything

03:54.280 --> 03:55.600
you shouldn't do in my car.

03:55.680 --> 03:56.680
Thank you.

03:57.400 --> 03:58.920
What shouldn't we do here?

03:59.000 --> 03:59.920
Just drive.

04:01.840 --> 04:03.040
What?

04:03.120 --> 04:05.080
Do you take me as your personal driver?

04:06.280 --> 04:08.360
Sang Yan, be honest with me.

04:08.440 --> 04:10.280
Do you envy us a lot?

04:11.120 --> 04:12.000
Fine, little demon.

04:12.080 --> 04:13.400
Jiaxu, let me ask you something.

04:13.480 --> 04:14.960
Back in our senior year of university,

04:15.040 --> 04:16.640
we moved dorms and my sister…

04:18.480 --> 04:19.560
Shut it.

04:19.640 --> 04:21.200
Let go.

04:21.800 --> 04:22.760
Just drive.

04:27.440 --> 04:28.280
All right.

04:28.360 --> 04:30.120
Welcome to Sang Yan's personal ride.

04:31.280 --> 04:32.960
Please fasten your seat belts.

04:33.040 --> 04:34.920
May I know if the temperature is okay?

04:35.000 --> 04:37.240
If so, please give me a five-star rating.

04:37.320 --> 04:39.560
- Today--
- Shut it. Just drive.

04:40.560 --> 04:42.360
Your brother talks a lot.

04:51.400 --> 04:52.400
I'm hungry.

04:52.480 --> 04:53.840
- You must be starving.
- In college--

04:53.920 --> 04:55.760
- I just ate.
- Here they come.

04:55.840 --> 04:56.760
Hurry up!

04:56.840 --> 04:57.920
We've been waiting for ages!

04:58.000 --> 04:58.960
What took you…

04:59.840 --> 05:00.960
What's going on?

05:01.040 --> 05:02.360
- Don't you know?
- I don't.

05:02.440 --> 05:03.360
I'm not telling you.

05:04.000 --> 05:05.200
Hello, guys.

05:05.280 --> 05:07.040
- Hi.
- Take your seats.

05:07.120 --> 05:08.120
Hello, Qian Fei.

05:09.200 --> 05:11.000
I forgot to introduce her.

05:11.080 --> 05:12.400
This is my girlfriend.

05:13.000 --> 05:14.240
Hold on.

05:15.000 --> 05:16.680
When we graduated,

05:16.760 --> 05:18.040
you two were taking photos.

05:18.120 --> 05:20.000
Wang Jun asked you who she is.

05:20.080 --> 05:21.360
You said she is your sister.

05:22.040 --> 05:23.200
That's right.

05:24.240 --> 05:25.760
Back then,

05:25.840 --> 05:27.000
I had a crush on her.

05:27.080 --> 05:28.400
I was too embarrassed to say it.

05:29.000 --> 05:30.280
- Sang Yan.
- Did you know?

05:30.360 --> 05:31.840
Sang Yan, are you and Jiaxu already…

05:31.920 --> 05:32.880
Yes.

05:32.960 --> 05:34.160
Order food already.

05:34.240 --> 05:35.400
I'm footing the bill tonight.

05:35.480 --> 05:36.600
I'm starving.

05:36.680 --> 05:37.760
- Excuse me!
- Menu, please.

05:38.840 --> 05:40.360
Do you have pork knuckles?

05:41.080 --> 05:42.560
You waited three months to tell us!

05:42.640 --> 05:44.040
- No, wait. Hear me out.
- Qian Fei!

05:44.120 --> 05:45.480
We should congratulate him.

05:45.560 --> 05:47.240
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

05:47.320 --> 05:48.800
This is too sudden. Thank you!

05:48.880 --> 05:49.800
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

05:49.880 --> 05:51.080
I was going to tell you.

05:51.160 --> 05:52.200
I'll go first.

05:52.280 --> 05:53.600
Take it easy.

05:53.680 --> 05:54.560
I'll be fine.

05:56.560 --> 05:58.560
So have you found a confinement center?

05:59.280 --> 06:00.720
No? What about the hospital?

06:00.800 --> 06:01.800
Private or public?

06:02.600 --> 06:03.560
Hold on.

06:04.080 --> 06:06.760
You should start
drawing up a budget, buddy.

06:06.840 --> 06:08.200
- Is it expensive?
- Yes.

06:08.280 --> 06:09.720
A premium center costs six figures.

06:09.800 --> 06:11.440
- Some charge over a million.
- Is that all?

06:11.520 --> 06:12.520
- Yes.
- Sang Yan.

06:13.560 --> 06:14.800
How do you know?

06:14.880 --> 06:15.960
She has a point.

06:17.080 --> 06:19.320
I'll have to know eventually.

06:19.400 --> 06:22.000
I did some research in advance.

06:22.080 --> 06:23.400
Why were you researching this?

06:24.520 --> 06:25.520
That's fishy.

06:25.600 --> 06:26.840
Forget about me.

06:26.920 --> 06:28.240
- Something is up.
- Forget it.

06:31.560 --> 06:33.120
Stop drinking. You've had enough.

06:33.200 --> 06:35.200
What do you mean? I barely had any.

06:36.320 --> 06:37.280
What's wrong?

06:37.360 --> 06:39.120
Can't my girlfriend have some wine?

06:39.200 --> 06:40.600
Can't I?

06:40.680 --> 06:41.600
Fine, as you wish.

06:41.680 --> 06:43.120
Your old boyfriend can deal with you.

06:43.680 --> 06:45.280
"Boyfriend" is enough.

06:45.360 --> 06:46.880
Why are you calling me old?

06:46.960 --> 06:48.280
It's hard on the ears.

06:48.360 --> 06:49.400
No, I mean it.

06:49.480 --> 06:51.320
She has to be home by ten.

06:51.920 --> 06:52.760
All right.

06:53.640 --> 06:54.720
Why should we listen to him?

06:55.840 --> 06:56.880
Are you feeling rebellious?

06:57.720 --> 06:58.800
Fine.

07:01.680 --> 07:02.640
The call went through.

07:04.480 --> 07:05.600
Hello, Mom.

07:07.120 --> 07:08.800
Sang Zhi called me a midget!

07:08.880 --> 07:10.640
- Keep it down.
- She even called me ugly.

07:10.720 --> 07:11.880
She even hit me.

07:11.960 --> 07:14.080
- Enough, buddy.
- That's so embarrassing.

07:14.160 --> 07:15.920
You are too old for this prank.

07:16.000 --> 07:18.040
I know. She will be home by ten.

07:19.280 --> 07:20.200
Qian Fei.

07:20.960 --> 07:22.160
Congratulations.

07:22.240 --> 07:23.520
- Drink up.
- Yes.

07:24.120 --> 07:26.320
- Bottoms up.
- Congratulations, Qian Fei.

07:26.400 --> 07:28.240
Your turn will come eventually.

07:28.320 --> 07:29.640
Eventually? Not anytime soon.

07:29.720 --> 07:30.640
It has to wait!

07:30.720 --> 07:31.800
Finish your wine.

07:32.720 --> 07:35.040
Enough with your feudal mindset. Be nice.

07:36.240 --> 07:37.160
Sang Yan.

07:38.040 --> 07:39.160
Ease up on the wine.

07:39.680 --> 07:40.680
How is your wine better?

07:42.880 --> 07:43.840
Okay, you've had enough.

08:02.320 --> 08:03.520
Are you eager to go home?

08:04.120 --> 08:05.200
No.

08:11.320 --> 08:14.560
Jiaxu, why didn't you drive today?

08:15.320 --> 08:17.320
It's quite a long walk from here.

08:18.200 --> 08:19.640
You drank too much wine.

08:20.160 --> 08:22.360
You can't go home reeking of wine.

08:33.880 --> 08:34.840
What's the matter?

08:35.960 --> 08:38.000
Are you really allergic to alcohol?

08:41.440 --> 08:42.640
Should we give it a try?

08:47.200 --> 08:48.520
Let's see

08:50.760 --> 08:51.920
if I'm allergic to it.

09:04.120 --> 09:05.960
I don't think I'm allergic anymore.

09:08.360 --> 09:09.840
I can give you a few more kisses.

09:17.240 --> 09:18.520
Hold on.

09:21.560 --> 09:22.800
This can't go on forever.

09:23.720 --> 09:24.640
I think

09:25.200 --> 09:26.680
I have to see you every day.

09:27.320 --> 09:28.920
If I don't see you for even a day,

09:29.000 --> 09:30.040
I'll miss you so badly.

09:51.120 --> 09:52.320
I'm heading home.

10:04.480 --> 10:05.400
Bye.

10:39.840 --> 10:41.080
Where were you?

10:42.080 --> 10:43.240
I took out the trash.

10:44.360 --> 10:46.000
Why did you come home so late?

10:47.880 --> 10:49.480
Sang Yan took me out to dinner.

10:50.840 --> 10:51.840
- Then…
- I'm going to sleep.

11:25.640 --> 11:26.640
What's wrong?

11:27.200 --> 11:28.240
Did you have wine?

11:32.480 --> 11:33.880
Just a little bit.

11:33.960 --> 11:34.880
I didn't drink much.

11:34.960 --> 11:36.440
Sang Yan was there anyway.

11:37.960 --> 11:40.200
I'll let it go since Sang Yan was there.

11:40.280 --> 11:41.560
But when you go out alone,

11:41.640 --> 11:42.560
do not drink.

11:50.120 --> 11:52.840
Are you and Duan Jiaxu dating?

11:57.600 --> 11:58.880
I saw everything.

12:05.440 --> 12:06.440
How long has it been?

12:13.080 --> 12:14.960
Not that long.

12:15.720 --> 12:17.880
I wanted to tell you.

12:18.840 --> 12:19.920
But…

12:20.000 --> 12:22.160
Is this why you didn't come home
for the summer?

12:25.600 --> 12:28.480
That was part of the reason.

12:29.240 --> 12:31.480
But it was also

12:31.560 --> 12:33.440
because I finally got an internship.

12:33.520 --> 12:36.160
I wanted to gain some experience
before I graduated.

12:38.720 --> 12:40.600
Did you stay at the dorm or his place

12:40.680 --> 12:41.680
over the summer?

12:41.760 --> 12:42.680
The dorm.

12:44.760 --> 12:45.640
It's true.

12:46.280 --> 12:47.560
Sang Yan came to Yihe.

12:47.640 --> 12:48.760
He knows everything.

12:58.800 --> 13:01.600
Mom, don't worry about it.

13:01.680 --> 13:03.840
Jiaxu treats me well.

13:03.920 --> 13:05.640
He is a kind person.

13:05.720 --> 13:07.280
You know him well.

13:07.360 --> 13:09.200
I know him. I know he is a good man.

13:10.200 --> 13:11.720
But do you know about his family?

13:14.160 --> 13:15.720
I don't know how it is now.

13:16.400 --> 13:17.960
Your brother told me before

13:19.680 --> 13:21.120
that his dad is in a coma.

13:21.880 --> 13:24.040
The victim's family
often gives them trouble.

13:24.120 --> 13:25.320
It's not really that often.

13:25.880 --> 13:27.160
Have you run into them?

13:32.720 --> 13:34.360
Jiaxu told me about it.

13:36.320 --> 13:37.880
You just took his word for it.

13:37.960 --> 13:39.760
You haven't seen it for yourself,
have you?

13:39.840 --> 13:42.480
I know he has been nice to you
since you were little.

13:43.280 --> 13:44.760
He was your tutor.

13:44.840 --> 13:45.960
I wonder

13:46.480 --> 13:48.840
if you've mistaken your admiration for him

13:49.400 --> 13:50.640
for love.

13:51.440 --> 13:53.760
You only see him as a brother, right?

13:54.880 --> 13:57.120
But if you two are in a relationship,

13:57.720 --> 13:59.080
your dad and I…

14:04.880 --> 14:06.000
I…

14:06.080 --> 14:07.440
I don't.

14:08.080 --> 14:09.800
I am an adult now.

14:09.880 --> 14:12.480
Would I not be able
to tell admiration from love?

14:13.160 --> 14:14.600
I really do like him.

14:15.240 --> 14:16.840
Zhizhi, you are only a young girl.

14:16.920 --> 14:17.880
You're still in college.

14:17.960 --> 14:18.800
But he's different.

14:18.880 --> 14:19.880
He's much older than you.

14:20.560 --> 14:22.600
He has a lot of experience as an adult.

14:22.680 --> 14:24.760
I know you won't like what I'm saying.

14:24.840 --> 14:26.400
We'll talk about it another time.

14:26.480 --> 14:27.560
Shower and go to bed.

14:44.120 --> 14:47.000
CHAPTER 23, STRANDED

14:47.080 --> 14:49.080
LOVE WITHOUT SECOND THOUGHTS

15:13.760 --> 15:14.720
Who do we have here?

15:15.760 --> 15:17.040
Where were you this morning?

15:18.880 --> 15:19.760
I…

15:21.680 --> 15:23.400
I did something very important.

15:24.520 --> 15:25.680
Something very important?

15:26.640 --> 15:27.680
What is it?

15:29.680 --> 15:31.280
You'll know soon enough.

15:31.920 --> 15:33.160
I can't tell you yet. All right?

15:39.640 --> 15:40.640
I've been thinking.

15:41.240 --> 15:43.240
You didn't go home all summer.

15:43.320 --> 15:45.040
Spend more time with your parents.

15:47.000 --> 15:48.080
What about you?

15:48.760 --> 15:49.800
I'll stay here too.

15:51.160 --> 15:52.280
I'm thinking

15:53.160 --> 15:54.440
I should pick a day

15:54.520 --> 15:56.800
to formally visit your parents.

15:59.760 --> 16:00.840
What do you think?

16:01.640 --> 16:02.920
I think it's a great idea.

16:03.520 --> 16:04.880
I'll ask them when I get back.

16:05.360 --> 16:07.640
And then we can go out for dinner.

16:09.520 --> 16:10.640
We can ask them.

16:12.120 --> 16:13.120
All right.

16:13.800 --> 16:14.640
Then let's go.

16:25.680 --> 16:27.320
I'll turn 20 next year.

16:33.560 --> 16:35.080
And I am almost 26.

16:36.760 --> 16:38.600
Time doesn't slow down for anyone.

16:41.000 --> 16:43.280
I'm not calling you old.

16:46.520 --> 16:47.680
I just think

16:49.400 --> 16:50.920
I am too young.

16:53.040 --> 16:55.040
I wish I weren't 20 years old.

16:55.600 --> 16:57.040
It would be great if I were 29.

16:58.400 --> 16:59.880
What makes you say that?

17:01.160 --> 17:03.880
I would be three years older than you

17:05.119 --> 17:06.280
if I were 29.

17:07.720 --> 17:08.640
That way…

17:10.400 --> 17:11.240
That way,

17:12.480 --> 17:14.240
my brother wouldn't have hit you

17:14.319 --> 17:16.040
for dating me.

17:24.240 --> 17:25.240
I can't allow that.

17:26.760 --> 17:28.160
I like younger girls.

17:32.240 --> 17:34.160
But I'll turn old someday.

17:35.320 --> 17:37.720
But you'll still be younger than me.

17:38.840 --> 17:40.040
What has gotten into you?

17:49.520 --> 17:50.560
Duan Jiaxu.

17:54.720 --> 17:55.840
Are you happy?

17:56.520 --> 17:57.960
Of course I am.

17:59.840 --> 18:01.040
Are you really happy?

18:01.640 --> 18:02.480
I really am.

18:04.000 --> 18:04.920
What's wrong?

18:06.400 --> 18:07.480
It's nothing.

18:07.560 --> 18:08.680
I'm glad to hear that.

18:10.560 --> 18:12.480
I want you to stay happy every day.

18:13.920 --> 18:15.040
I will make sure

18:15.120 --> 18:17.120
you are happy every day of your life.

18:19.800 --> 18:21.040
Okay.

18:21.120 --> 18:22.520
That will depend on you.

18:23.400 --> 18:25.360
We'll see if you'll keep staying with me.

18:45.720 --> 18:46.920
Here you go.

18:47.000 --> 18:48.560
Xiaoduan, have some tea.

18:48.640 --> 18:49.480
Thank you, Mr. Sang.

18:49.560 --> 18:50.680
Take a seat.

18:51.760 --> 18:53.680
Don't act like a stranger.

18:53.760 --> 18:54.880
Did you bring me tea leaves?

18:55.440 --> 18:57.000
You like tea.

18:57.080 --> 18:58.120
I don't know much about it.

18:58.200 --> 18:59.880
I thought you could appraise them.

19:01.160 --> 19:02.080
Very well.

19:03.200 --> 19:06.320
I asked you to come here

19:06.400 --> 19:07.480
while Zhizhi is away today.

19:07.560 --> 19:08.600
I know it was sudden.

19:08.680 --> 19:10.760
I hope you don't mind.

19:11.280 --> 19:12.120
I don't.

19:12.200 --> 19:13.400
I was planning

19:13.480 --> 19:15.760
to visit you and Mrs. Sang in person soon.

19:16.920 --> 19:17.800
Honestly,

19:18.280 --> 19:20.200
I was a little surprised when I found out

19:20.280 --> 19:21.560
that you and Zhizhi are dating.

19:23.800 --> 19:25.920
I wanted to inform you personally.

19:26.840 --> 19:28.320
I talked to her

19:28.400 --> 19:29.520
about some issues.

19:30.200 --> 19:32.000
But she doesn't seem to get it.

19:32.920 --> 19:34.640
Her mom and I have been thinking.

19:34.720 --> 19:35.920
Since you are in Nanwu,

19:36.000 --> 19:37.840
we might as well ask you to come here,

19:37.920 --> 19:39.520
so we can discuss it face-to-face.

19:42.160 --> 19:43.360
Mr. Sang,

19:43.440 --> 19:45.280
is there anything that concerns you?

19:45.360 --> 19:46.440
Feel free to ask me.

19:47.880 --> 19:48.920
That is great.

19:49.640 --> 19:51.600
How long have you and Zhizhi been dating?

19:52.280 --> 19:54.240
We started dating in May.

19:54.320 --> 19:56.440
It has been less than a year.

19:57.720 --> 19:59.840
It hasn't been that long.

20:01.040 --> 20:02.480
Sang Yan told me

20:02.560 --> 20:04.640
that you've settled your family affairs.

20:04.720 --> 20:06.520
- Is that right?
- Yes.

20:06.600 --> 20:08.840
Did that family cause you
any more trouble?

20:08.920 --> 20:10.440
Not recently.

20:11.440 --> 20:14.440
So how is your dad doing lately?

20:16.400 --> 20:17.240
He is

20:17.960 --> 20:19.240
still the same.

20:19.320 --> 20:20.680
He's still bedridden.

20:22.520 --> 20:23.440
I'm sorry.

20:24.200 --> 20:25.120
It's okay.

20:27.120 --> 20:28.200
Xiaoduan.

20:28.280 --> 20:29.960
You've always been good to Zhizhi.

20:30.040 --> 20:31.120
You've taken care of her.

20:31.200 --> 20:33.200
Her mom and I are grateful for that.

20:33.920 --> 20:36.080
But if you want to be
in a relationship with her,

20:36.760 --> 20:38.360
given the circumstances of your family,

20:39.160 --> 20:40.360
her mom and I

20:41.680 --> 20:44.120
are indeed a bit concerned.

20:45.840 --> 20:47.120
Zhizhi is still young.

20:47.200 --> 20:48.800
Maybe she hasn't thought that far ahead

20:48.880 --> 20:50.240
about this relationship.

20:51.040 --> 20:52.560
However,

20:52.640 --> 20:54.760
if you two are in a relationship…

20:55.680 --> 20:57.400
After all, we are her parents.

20:57.480 --> 20:58.720
We are worried.

21:00.920 --> 21:01.880
I understand.

21:01.960 --> 21:04.080
I can relate to that, Mr. Sang.

21:04.840 --> 21:06.600
All the concerns you have

21:06.680 --> 21:08.360
are things that I should consider.

21:09.840 --> 21:11.240
But you have my word.

21:11.320 --> 21:12.280
I will

21:12.840 --> 21:14.360
resolve all of these issues.

21:16.840 --> 21:18.160
I believe you on this.

21:18.240 --> 21:20.920
I'm only expressing my concerns.

21:21.520 --> 21:22.880
This might sound hurtful to you.

21:22.960 --> 21:24.480
I hope you understand.

21:24.560 --> 21:25.760
It's okay.

21:25.840 --> 21:27.080
After all,

21:27.720 --> 21:29.360
we've doted on Zhizhi all her life.

21:30.200 --> 21:31.800
It pains us to see her suffer.

21:33.040 --> 21:33.920
Yes.

21:37.280 --> 21:39.040
Zhizhi isn't even 20 yet.

21:39.520 --> 21:40.800
You are a bit older than her.

21:42.160 --> 21:43.400
I truly hope

21:43.960 --> 21:45.840
that you can seriously consider

21:46.400 --> 21:47.720
your future with her.

21:48.480 --> 21:49.360
Is that clear?

21:49.880 --> 21:50.880
Yes, Mr. Sang.

22:10.080 --> 22:11.480
I'm home.

22:11.560 --> 22:12.640
Welcome home.

22:12.720 --> 22:14.080
How was the classmate gathering?

22:14.600 --> 22:16.080
It was not bad.

22:17.000 --> 22:17.960
I just feel

22:18.520 --> 22:19.960
that everyone has changed

22:20.880 --> 22:22.400
quite a lot.

22:22.480 --> 22:23.400
Is that so?

22:25.440 --> 22:26.520
Let me get it for you.

22:33.440 --> 22:34.800
I'll help you slice the fruit, Mom.

22:35.440 --> 22:37.480
No need. Talk to your dad.

22:37.560 --> 22:38.440
I can manage.

22:39.240 --> 22:41.640
What did we do to deserve
such a lovely daughter?

22:43.840 --> 22:46.240
I've been thinking about the past.

22:47.600 --> 22:49.520
I remember you were weak as a child.

22:50.240 --> 22:51.960
You often had a cold or fever.

22:52.040 --> 22:53.560
Your mom and I

22:53.640 --> 22:55.080
went to the hospital every other day.

22:56.200 --> 22:58.200
You would cry as soon
as we entered the hospital.

22:58.920 --> 23:00.800
Seeing you in pain pained us just as much.

23:00.880 --> 23:02.160
But there was no other way.

23:03.520 --> 23:06.040
Your brother was only a little boy.

23:07.200 --> 23:08.680
He didn't like having a new addition.

23:08.760 --> 23:10.440
He felt that we neglected him

23:10.520 --> 23:11.880
after you came along.

23:11.960 --> 23:14.160
I remember he wrote in his diary,

23:14.240 --> 23:15.680
"I would rather have a dog

23:15.760 --> 23:17.120
than this sister."

23:18.120 --> 23:19.840
But when you were in the hospital

23:19.920 --> 23:20.880
and he couldn't see you,

23:20.960 --> 23:22.240
he kept following me around

23:22.320 --> 23:23.760
and asking me where you were.

23:23.840 --> 23:25.440
One day, I told him

23:25.520 --> 23:26.760
that we had gotten rid of you.

23:27.560 --> 23:28.960
He was so scared that he cried.

23:31.200 --> 23:33.160
That is an amusing memory.

23:33.760 --> 23:35.800
It feels like it happened yesterday.

23:36.920 --> 23:39.200
And now, you and your brother
are grown-ups.

23:39.680 --> 23:41.280
You're turning 20 next year.

23:42.880 --> 23:44.280
You've also started dating.

23:44.960 --> 23:45.920
In a few years,

23:46.680 --> 23:47.840
you'll get married.

23:59.480 --> 24:00.400
Yes.

24:00.920 --> 24:02.840
Time flies like an arrow.

24:05.520 --> 24:06.520
Zhizhi.

24:07.080 --> 24:08.760
I am not a snobbish person.

24:09.240 --> 24:11.600
I don't think
that we're superior to others

24:11.680 --> 24:13.840
simply because we are comfortably off.

24:14.360 --> 24:16.720
I'm not saying that no one deserves you.

24:16.800 --> 24:17.640
Of course,

24:17.720 --> 24:19.200
if anyone wants to be your boyfriend,

24:19.280 --> 24:21.520
I am certain I can find his flaws.

24:22.360 --> 24:23.520
I'm not saying

24:23.600 --> 24:25.200
you are too fragile to undergo hardships.

24:26.160 --> 24:27.160
But your mom and I

24:28.240 --> 24:29.680
really hate to see you suffer.

24:30.320 --> 24:32.480
We don't want you to have a hard life.

24:32.560 --> 24:34.760
We will always have that kind of worry.

24:35.840 --> 24:37.120
Don't worry, Dad.

24:37.200 --> 24:38.800
I am not suffering any hardships.

24:38.880 --> 24:41.360
I am very happy every day.

24:42.880 --> 24:43.800
I'm glad to hear that.

24:44.760 --> 24:46.880
I think of myself as a normal parent.

24:46.960 --> 24:47.920
I am the same

24:48.000 --> 24:49.280
as every other dad.

24:49.360 --> 24:51.280
I only hope that my daughter

24:51.360 --> 24:53.520
can have a smooth life free from any harm.

24:53.600 --> 24:56.040
I want you to be safe and happy.

24:58.520 --> 24:59.400
Zhizhi.

24:59.480 --> 25:00.320
Thanks, Mom.

25:03.560 --> 25:04.800
I wasn't going

25:04.880 --> 25:05.960
to tell you this

25:06.760 --> 25:08.840
because I was afraid you might get upset

25:08.920 --> 25:09.880
and hold it against us.

25:10.960 --> 25:11.880
Today,

25:12.560 --> 25:14.240
I asked Jiaxu to come here

25:14.320 --> 25:15.640
while you were away.

25:29.960 --> 25:31.640
You mentioned

25:32.320 --> 25:35.040
that we would talk…

25:35.560 --> 25:37.080
in person together.

25:37.600 --> 25:38.480
Isn't that right?

25:40.040 --> 25:41.960
So what did you talk about

25:43.320 --> 25:44.960
while I was away?

25:46.280 --> 25:47.720
I told him the concerns

25:47.800 --> 25:50.120
that your mom and I were having.

25:50.760 --> 25:51.920
What I told him

25:52.520 --> 25:54.760
may have been hurtful in some ways.

25:54.840 --> 25:57.040
But he said
that he would seriously consider

25:57.120 --> 25:57.960
your future together.

25:59.120 --> 26:00.160
You might think

26:01.320 --> 26:03.760
it's unnecessary
to think that far ahead right now.

26:04.720 --> 26:06.880
But if you want to be together
in the long run,

26:07.440 --> 26:08.920
I want you to think it through,

26:09.840 --> 26:11.920
given his current family circumstances.

26:12.480 --> 26:14.240
If you think it's not the right fit,

26:15.240 --> 26:16.760
it would be better to break up.

26:18.560 --> 26:19.480
Yes, Zhizhi.

26:20.080 --> 26:21.440
If you can't bring yourself

26:21.520 --> 26:22.800
to tell Duan Jiaxu,

26:22.880 --> 26:24.320
we can tell him on your behalf.

26:27.280 --> 26:28.160
This…

26:46.920 --> 26:48.920
I know you think I can't handle

26:50.440 --> 26:52.000
the slightest challenge in life.

26:54.080 --> 26:56.360
But he hasn't brought me any hardships.

27:00.840 --> 27:02.960
And the thing is,

27:04.000 --> 27:06.080
despite his family's circumstances

27:06.760 --> 27:08.280
and his bedridden dad,

27:08.360 --> 27:10.720
I'm willing to face everything
with him together.

27:11.560 --> 27:12.800
I am willing to shoulder it.

27:13.360 --> 27:15.440
Our relationship wasn't formed on a whim.

27:16.600 --> 27:18.880
We went through a lot of considerations.

27:20.960 --> 27:22.200
But can you please

27:23.160 --> 27:24.720
not hold a prejudice against him?

27:31.760 --> 27:34.680
What happened to his family
wasn't his choice.

27:36.080 --> 27:38.480
He has suffered a lot of prejudices.

27:40.560 --> 27:41.880
I never imagined

27:43.400 --> 27:45.240
that you would…

27:48.560 --> 27:50.440
Your dad and I are just worried--

27:50.520 --> 27:52.000
I'm tired.

27:52.080 --> 27:53.480
I'm going to my room.

27:58.160 --> 27:59.360
This…

28:22.040 --> 28:23.240
Xiaoduan.

28:23.320 --> 28:24.840
You've always been good to Zhizhi.

28:24.920 --> 28:26.040
You've taken care of her.

28:26.120 --> 28:27.960
Her mom and I are grateful for that.

28:28.480 --> 28:30.600
But if you want to be
in a relationship with her,

28:31.280 --> 28:32.880
given the circumstances of your family,

28:33.720 --> 28:34.880
her mom and I

28:36.200 --> 28:38.320
are indeed a bit concerned.

29:16.520 --> 29:19.120
Why would they say those things to Jiaxu?

29:20.560 --> 29:22.680
He must feel a lot of pressure.

29:29.120 --> 29:31.160
What should I say to him?

30:04.840 --> 30:05.880
Hello?

30:15.160 --> 30:16.040
Hello?

30:17.680 --> 30:18.760
Was it an accidental dial?

30:21.160 --> 30:22.000
No.

30:22.960 --> 30:23.880
What's wrong?

30:25.560 --> 30:27.760
Why aren't you saying anything?

30:31.280 --> 30:32.120
Sorry.

30:34.520 --> 30:36.720
Whatever they said,

30:36.800 --> 30:39.120
don't take it to heart.

30:39.800 --> 30:40.640
So

30:41.400 --> 30:42.520
don't be upset.

30:47.960 --> 30:50.560
I'm not upset.

30:51.960 --> 30:54.120
Your parents didn't say anything hurtful.

30:54.200 --> 30:55.400
They were nice.

30:57.240 --> 30:58.200
But it's true.

30:59.160 --> 31:01.040
They did express some of their concerns.

31:05.120 --> 31:06.480
What concerns?

31:06.560 --> 31:08.760
They think I am too old.

31:08.840 --> 31:10.040
It will be embarrassing

31:10.120 --> 31:11.400
when we go out together.

31:13.280 --> 31:14.520
Did you talk about this?

31:19.240 --> 31:21.160
Stop joking around.

31:21.240 --> 31:22.680
I am serious.

31:22.760 --> 31:24.200
It was nothing.

31:25.080 --> 31:27.680
Your dad told me a lot of things.

31:27.760 --> 31:30.560
I'm not sure which of them you mean.

31:32.320 --> 31:33.280
I mean

31:34.440 --> 31:37.040
the part where they told you
to reconsider.

31:46.280 --> 31:47.400
Well…

31:51.200 --> 31:53.160
Don't you have any questions for me?

31:54.760 --> 31:55.960
Or maybe

31:57.160 --> 31:58.920
is there something you would like to say?

32:03.320 --> 32:04.440
Sang Zhi.

32:05.960 --> 32:07.240
I'm just asking.

32:07.720 --> 32:09.080
It doesn't matter anyway.

32:13.680 --> 32:15.120
I'm calling

32:16.080 --> 32:17.400
because I want you to know

32:19.520 --> 32:20.760
that you are great.

32:23.360 --> 32:24.360
As you know,

32:25.560 --> 32:27.640
they always think I am too young.

32:28.280 --> 32:30.080
That's why they are concerned.

32:31.960 --> 32:33.320
But thankfully, it's you.

32:35.240 --> 32:36.560
If it were anyone else,

32:37.520 --> 32:38.880
they would have a lot more to say.

32:40.440 --> 32:41.320
I know.

32:42.720 --> 32:43.560
By the way,

32:44.200 --> 32:45.360
as I've told you,

32:45.440 --> 32:46.800
what happened to your family

32:46.880 --> 32:48.560
has nothing to do with you.

32:50.800 --> 32:52.000
Don't blame yourself.

32:53.440 --> 32:54.640
Besides,

32:54.720 --> 32:56.040
whatever happens to your dad,

32:56.120 --> 32:57.840
we can shoulder it together.

32:58.520 --> 32:59.800
We can look after him together.

33:02.160 --> 33:03.800
I know all of that.

33:05.920 --> 33:08.240
Don't say anything rash to them.

33:08.920 --> 33:10.640
You finally get to take a break.

33:10.720 --> 33:12.120
Spend time with your parents.

33:12.800 --> 33:15.400
Do not let this matter affect your mood.

33:17.000 --> 33:17.880
All right.

33:17.960 --> 33:19.280
Stop thinking about it.

33:19.840 --> 33:21.800
Go to sleep. Okay?

33:23.840 --> 33:25.080
- Okay.
- One more thing.

33:25.160 --> 33:27.280
I have to head back to Yihe

33:27.360 --> 33:28.800
tomorrow morning.

33:29.520 --> 33:30.480
Head back

33:31.280 --> 33:32.200
to Yihe?

33:33.240 --> 33:34.800
I just received a phone call.

33:34.880 --> 33:37.360
I have to meet a client for work tomorrow,

33:37.440 --> 33:38.720
so I have to head back.

33:38.800 --> 33:39.640
Then

33:40.200 --> 33:41.760
I'll go with you.

33:42.680 --> 33:44.760
Don't. The flight is tomorrow morning.

33:44.840 --> 33:45.760
It's very early.

33:46.240 --> 33:47.760
Stay home and sleep tight.

33:47.840 --> 33:48.880
Let me see you off.

33:50.280 --> 33:51.680
You really don't have to.

33:52.240 --> 33:53.120
I'm a grown man.

33:53.200 --> 33:54.560
I can go to the airport on my own.

33:56.560 --> 33:57.720
All right.

33:57.800 --> 33:59.440
Stop thinking about it. I mean it.

34:00.360 --> 34:02.160
Go to sleep. Okay?

34:05.520 --> 34:06.400
Okay.

34:08.400 --> 34:09.320
Good night.

34:13.080 --> 34:14.159
Good night.

34:28.760 --> 34:31.080
Why is he leaving all of a sudden?

34:33.920 --> 34:35.679
Is he avoiding me?

34:37.760 --> 34:39.840
Is he really considering

34:40.960 --> 34:42.280
breaking up with me?

34:46.239 --> 34:48.440
What is on his mind?

35:05.520 --> 35:07.280
Zhizhi, are you going out?

35:09.720 --> 35:11.640
- Why is your suitcase--
- I'm heading back to Yihe.

35:12.520 --> 35:14.200
Why are you going back all of a sudden?

35:15.080 --> 35:16.560
I'm going to talk to Jiaxu.

35:17.040 --> 35:18.280
I have something to tell him.

35:21.680 --> 35:23.040
I already booked a plane ticket.

35:23.120 --> 35:24.000
Don't worry about me.

35:24.080 --> 35:25.080
Zhizhi.

35:26.360 --> 35:27.960
Did what we said last night

35:28.040 --> 35:29.280
make you upset?

35:29.360 --> 35:30.280
Is that it?

35:31.640 --> 35:32.760
No.

35:33.360 --> 35:35.280
I understand your concerns.

35:35.360 --> 35:36.600
I know you mean well.

35:37.880 --> 35:39.200
But I think…

35:42.120 --> 35:43.360
I'm a grown-up now.

35:44.720 --> 35:45.920
I'm not a kid anymore.

35:46.480 --> 35:48.880
I am very sure of what I want.

35:51.040 --> 35:52.440
So I want to fight for it.

35:55.320 --> 35:56.200
Zhizhi.

35:57.320 --> 36:00.200
We are both very fond of Xiaoduan.

36:00.280 --> 36:02.160
But we have our concerns.

36:02.760 --> 36:04.280
Your dad and I have lived a long life.

36:04.960 --> 36:07.080
We can see clearly

36:07.840 --> 36:10.240
about a lot of things
and people in this world.

36:10.320 --> 36:12.440
I know you don't trust Duan Jiaxu.

36:15.160 --> 36:17.280
But can you trust me for once?

36:26.920 --> 36:28.120
We'll drive you to the airport.

37:08.200 --> 37:09.360
Hello, Jiaxu.

37:09.440 --> 37:10.320
Zhizhi.

37:11.040 --> 37:12.200
Your brother just told me

37:12.280 --> 37:13.480
that you're coming back today.

37:14.840 --> 37:17.600
Yes, I'm already at the airport.

37:17.680 --> 37:18.560
Okay.

37:19.040 --> 37:20.040
Wait there for me.

37:22.200 --> 37:23.040
Okay.

37:38.080 --> 37:39.120
Sang Zhi.

37:39.200 --> 37:40.680
He did the right thing.

37:41.320 --> 37:43.120
You're too young right now.

37:43.200 --> 37:44.760
This isn't right. Got it?

37:46.520 --> 37:48.120
But I will grow up.

37:48.200 --> 37:50.240
Then let's wait until you grow up.

37:50.320 --> 37:51.480
But when I grow up,

37:51.560 --> 37:53.240
he'll fall for someone else.

38:04.920 --> 38:05.880
This time,

38:07.400 --> 38:08.840
I definitely won't cry.

38:13.800 --> 38:14.680
Zhizhi.

38:18.000 --> 38:20.040
Why didn't you tell me
you were coming back?

38:25.640 --> 38:26.800
What's wrong?

38:29.240 --> 38:30.640
Do you remember

38:34.040 --> 38:35.760
I came to Yihe when I was in 11th grade

38:38.120 --> 38:39.800
to meet up with my online crush?

38:43.400 --> 38:44.480
Actually,

38:45.120 --> 38:46.960
I didn't have an online crush.

38:49.720 --> 38:51.640
I came to Yihe to see you.

39:01.120 --> 39:03.040
I heard from my brother

39:05.280 --> 39:06.760
that you had a girlfriend.

39:08.280 --> 39:10.520
That's why I came to Yihe.

39:13.240 --> 39:14.920
I wanted to see you.

39:19.800 --> 39:21.480
I didn't start liking you

39:21.560 --> 39:23.960
only after I came to Yihe for college.

39:25.880 --> 39:27.240
I lied to you.

39:29.320 --> 39:31.680
I didn't want you to think…

39:33.400 --> 39:34.600
To think that…

39:37.360 --> 39:38.480
What is it?

39:39.720 --> 39:41.480
That I was weird.

39:48.520 --> 39:49.400
That…

39:56.640 --> 39:57.840
This is

39:58.840 --> 40:00.920
the secret I wrote when I was little.

40:01.520 --> 40:02.440
It's inside.

40:24.240 --> 40:25.720
I have a secret.

40:26.240 --> 40:28.440
I don't want to admit it,

40:30.400 --> 40:31.520
but

40:31.600 --> 40:32.800
I seem

40:32.880 --> 40:34.640
to have fallen for him.

40:35.320 --> 40:37.600
Duan Jiaxu.

40:38.200 --> 40:41.160
Before I even knew how to spell your name,

40:45.120 --> 40:46.640
I've already liked you.

40:46.720 --> 40:48.480
DUAN JIAXU

40:48.560 --> 40:50.680
I've liked you for a very long time.

40:52.040 --> 40:53.040
I HAVE A SECRET

40:53.120 --> 40:55.520
I DON'T WANT TO ADMIT IT,
BUT I SEEM TO HAVE FALLEN FOR HIM

40:55.600 --> 40:56.760
DUAN JIAXU

41:06.760 --> 41:08.320
Make a lot of money

41:08.400 --> 41:09.680
and help him pay off his debts.

41:09.760 --> 41:10.600
MAKE A LOT OF MONEY

41:10.680 --> 41:11.880
AND HELP HIM PAY OFF HIS DEBTS.

41:25.000 --> 41:26.200
I am telling you

41:26.680 --> 41:29.440
the secret I wanted to seal away forever.

41:30.840 --> 41:31.680
Can you…

41:36.600 --> 41:37.880
Can you believe

41:37.960 --> 41:39.680
that you are a great person?

41:42.800 --> 41:44.240
Seeing how much

41:45.040 --> 41:46.600
I like you,

41:48.240 --> 41:51.240
can you ignore what people say about you?

41:54.560 --> 41:56.920
Can you be with me forever?

42:03.960 --> 42:04.880
Please?

42:26.600 --> 42:29.920
Are you referring
to the 118-square-meter unit?

42:30.680 --> 42:32.920
It's available for viewing
tomorrow morning, yes?

42:33.000 --> 42:34.200
Okay.

42:34.720 --> 42:36.320
I'll contact you then.

42:37.840 --> 42:39.080
Thank you.

42:55.080 --> 42:55.960
Hello?

42:56.040 --> 42:57.080
Hello? Where are you now?

42:57.560 --> 42:59.120
I'm on my way. I'll be there soon.

42:59.200 --> 43:00.680
How much longer, sir?

43:02.160 --> 43:03.040
Five minutes.

43:03.120 --> 43:04.440
As if I would believe you!

43:04.520 --> 43:06.240
Sang Yan hasn't even picked you up yet!

43:06.800 --> 43:08.160
I'm here already.

43:08.240 --> 43:09.320
Just get here now!

43:09.400 --> 43:10.320
Busted.

43:11.680 --> 43:12.840
Bye.

43:12.920 --> 43:13.760
Bye.
